{"badges":["TM31","TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Divide puff pastry into 2 equal pieces and refrigerate until needed.","Place garlic cloves and oil in mixing bowl and chop <b>3 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula","Cook <b>7 min\/100°C\/speed <b>. Transfer to a bowl and set aside.","Place water in mixing bowl. Place button mushrooms in Varoma, sprinkle with herbs, salt and pepper. Place Varoma into position and steam <b>10 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>.","Stir mushrooms with spatula to ensure even cooking. Steam a further <b>10 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>. Remove Varoma and set aside. Empty mixing bowl.","Preheat oven to 200°C. Line the base of a tart tin (Ø 26 cm) with baking paper and set aside.","Using a rolling pin, roll out one piece of pastry on a lightly floured surface. Line prepared tart tin with pastry and set aside. Roll out second piece of pastry and gently score its surface with the point of a sharp knife, making a criss-cross pattern without cutting through the dough. In the centre of the pastry, cut a cross and fold back its corners to create a small opening. Set aside. Spread mushrooms in pastry-lined tart tin.","Place reserved cooked garlic, eggs, flour and crème fraîche in mixing bowl and cook <b>5 min\/80°C\/speed 2<b>, then blend <b>10 sec\/speed 6<b>.","Pour sauce over mushrooms, cover pie with second pastry disc, seal well around the edges, brush pie surface with milk and bake for 30-35 minutes (200°C), or until golden brown. Serve hot or warm."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["400 g puff pastry","4 garlic cloves","10 g oil","300 g water","750 g fresh button mushrooms, cut in slices","2 tsp dried herbes de Provence","½ tsp salt, adjust to taste","¼ tsp ground black pepper, adjust to taste","2 eggs","20 g plain flour","50 g crème fraîche","10 g milk, for glazing"]}],"id":"r151916","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-FR9dNIwz_Ck\/XZWdq6ltvqI\/AAAAAAAAeo4\/-f6urkAQcyUXOMXLbKDpaCZfIjbIJdcwQCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_L3J5MrooPR-OV94R.png","title":"Mushroom pie","publishedAt":"2018-04-10T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"12 g","fat":"22 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"28 g","calories":"1476 kJ \/ 353 kcal"},"usefulItems":"tart tin (Ø 26 cm), baking paper, rolling pin, pastry brush, oven","hintsAndTricks":["Combine button mushrooms with other mushroom varieties (e.g. porcini, chanterelles, crimini, portobello, morels, shiitake)."],"basicInfo":["medium","25m","1h 30m","6 portions"]}